Freshly baked muffins are one of the easiest and quickest baked treats to create, and these blueberry cream cheese muffins are a perfect and unique way to enjoy the classic and internationally loved blueberry muffin. Bake a larger batch of these scrumptious muffins to enjoy throughout the week, or to gift to your loved ones as a heartfelt yummy gesture.  Streusel crumble topping Blueberry muffins  Cream cheese fillings Glaze  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Stir fried beef with ginger and garlic This recipe was found on omgchocolatedesserts.com